highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 340 weeks straight.
“Faz um Vuk Vuk (Teto Espelhado)” by MC Kevin o Chris, Dj Nk Da Serra, and Mc Magrinho is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 107 spots at #65.
Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Cruel Summer” is the highest at #4.
“Paint The Town Red” by Doja Cat is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #22.
